==English==
===Adjective===
'''riparian'''
# Of or related to the bank of a [[river]].


=== Derived terms ===

# In legal terms a ‘'''riparian right'''’ is defined as the right to use water for household purposes and for the watering of a domestic garden, although the precise definition varies between jurisdictions.  A riparian right may also embody the absolute right to control and use water in a stream or creek.